LAMMPS (22 Jul 2025 - Update 3)
OMP_NUM_THREADS environment is not set. Defaulting to 1 thread.
  using 1 OpenMP thread(s) per MPI task
# Corte (shear xy) de diamante PERFECTO (sin falla) -- CONTROL.
# Misma orientacion y mismas condiciones que in.shear_SF. La unica diferencia
# fisica es la AUSENCIA de la falla de apilamiento: sirve para demostrar que es
# la falla la que nuclea la plasticidad (el perfecto debe ceder mas tarde / a
# mayor pxy, por inestabilidad homogenea).

#(1) Inicializacion
units		metal
dimension	3
boundary	p p p
atom_style	atomic

# --------------------- DEFINICION DE ATOMOS ---------------------
read_data SampleSTF_perfect        # <-- cristal perfecto, misma orientacion
Reading data file ...
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (43.68665 61.782252 50.444998)
  1 by 3 by 2 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  24000 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.055 seconds

set group all type 1
Setting atom values ...
  24000 settings made for type
group C type 1
24000 atoms in group C
mass 1 12.01

#(3) Potencial
pair_style tersoff
pair_coeff * * ./SiC_1994.tersoff C C C C C C
Reading tersoff potential file ./SiC_1994.tersoff with DATE: 2011-05-03

#(4) Minimizacion / relajacion de caja
thermo 100
write_data data_perfect.ini
